	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Varia sunt et perplexa, quae nunciantur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam nostri aliquando saperent; piscator ictus sapit, hi toties icti ne nunc quidem sapere volunt.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed nitor divina providentia, quae me unice sustentat; scit ipse, quorsum haec omnia destinet.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p629">Coignetius</persName> et nunciat multa fausta; sed bonus vir et ipse falsus est.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogo te, si quando ad eum scribis, meis verbis salvere eum iubeas siginificesque literas eius mihi redditas.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil habeo, quod rescribam, et inanes mittere nolo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tibi quoque mirum accidere non debet, si rarius posthac scribo; quid enim hoc unum toties scriberem me nihil habere, quod scribam, praesertim ad te alioquin occupatissimum.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid certi et digni habuero, officio meo non deero.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si tantum a te postulare debeo, rogo te, mi venerande pater, tu caeteris colophonem addas et veri aliquid (quod iam deinceps constare omnino poterit) de hoc incerto rerum eventu nos edoceas; ego bona spe non destituor.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p18507" cert="high">Herculi</persName> tuas reddidi; nam hic est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Agit gratias, te cum tuis salvum cupit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Instant nuptiae operosissimae, in quibus concionandum; ideo sum brevior.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, reverende in Christo pater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Yetz, yetz ze aabet umb die 4 ist der <persName type="citizen_name">fasel</persName> mit großem pomp yngeritten, darunder vyl <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l646">Glarner</placeName> und <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8108">Gilg Tschudi</persName>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Bin ich von <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1770">G[regorio] C[arlin]</persName>, mit dem mir 3 wort ze reden kum wil worden, gewarnet, wie <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8108">G[ilg] Tsch[udi]</persName> allein kommen, ettwas mütery und pratick ze machen, und wie er ein schryben schon yetz uff dem wäg ußgoßen, so im von dem apt von <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l970">Einsidlen</placeName> von <placeName ref="l1107" cert="high">Trient</placeName> geschriben, wie der <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8621">Conde den Guisen</persName> den fuͦßfal thon und die sach ires theils in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464">Franckrych</placeName> nunmee eroberet.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Doch so werde ich schryben deren dingen halb von h[erren] landtaman <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p252">Bäldi</persName> han; den brieff bringt houptman <persName type="auto_name">Häßi</persName>.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas, cum haec scriberem, nondum accepi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu vigila, ut verum habeamus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8108">Tsch[udius]</persName>spargat in nuptiis, omnia expiscabor interim.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der apt von <placeName ref="l1618" cert="high">Pfäfers</placeName> ist ouch hie.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si <placeName type="auto_name">Condensis</placeName> opus haberet milite, velim omnino rationem haberi <persName type="auto_name">Carlini</persName>; sunt huius consilii mei gravissimae causae.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vellem et ad illum perscribi; velim simultati inter magnos viros nullam occasionem dari.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">20. iulii anno 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8009" cert="high">F[abricius</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amplissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, d. et patri suo in Christo reverendo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
